channel.title: How do I x-log myself in runescape?
channel.description: basically, I've been boxing using a script to see me through the night and whilst I'm out places. I've come back to have my wins high but small rewards. I've seen and had happen to me people teleporting back out of the arena with 50m+ stakes. I've seen several methods of this being done untill 1st oct 2012. What do I have to do to make myself log the arena?

item.title: How do I x-log myself in runescape?
